    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a wizard, you gain the following class features.</p><h3>Hit Points</h3><p><strong>Hit Dice:</strong> 1d6 per wizard level<br /><strong>Hit Points at 1st Level:</strong> 6 + your Constitution modifier<br /><strong>Hit Points at Higher Levels:</strong> 1d6 (or 4) + your Constitution modifier per wizard level after 1st</p><h3>Proficiencies</h3><p><strong>Armor:</strong> None<br /><strong>Weapons:</strong> Daggers, darts, light crossbows, quarterstaffs, sickle, slings<br /><strong>Tools:</strong> None<br /><strong>Saving Throws:</strong> Intelligence, Wisdom<br /><strong>Skills:</strong> Choose two from Arcana, History, Insight, Investigation, Medicine, and Religion</p><h1>Wizard Advancement</h1><table><thead><tr><th>Level</th><th>Proficiency Bonus</th><th>Features</th><th>Cantrips Known</th><th>1st</th><th>2nd</th><th>3rd</th><th>4th</th><th>5th</th><th>6th</th><th>7th</th><th>8th</th><th>9th</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1st</td><td>+2</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.vixkTDWjBHmkqEoJ]{Spellcasting (Spellbook)}, @UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.hrPTVCw4wS82wZIy]{Arcane Recovery}</td><td>3</td><td>2</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>-</td></tr><tr><td>2nd</td><td>+2</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.bTAoBU4Udq5d5Hv1]{Arcane Tradition}</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>-</td></tr><tr><td>3rd</td><td>+2</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.v0Cswe1u3tY1qUUf]{Cantrip Formulas}</td><td>3</td><td>4</td><td>2</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>-</td></tr><tr><td>4th</td><td>+2</td><td>Ability Score Improvement</td><td>4</td><td>4</td><td>3</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>-</td></tr><tr><td>5th</td><td>+3</td><td>—</td><td>4</td><td>4</td><td>3</td><td>2</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>-</td></tr><tr><td>6th</td><td>+3</td><td>Arcane Tradition Feature</td><td>4</td><td>4</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td colspan=\"2\">-</td></tr><tr><td>7th</td><td>+3</td><td>—</td><td>4</td><td>4</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>1</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>-</td></tr><tr><td>8th</td><td>+3</td><td>Ability Score Improvement</td><td>4</td><td>4</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>2</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>-</td></tr><tr><td>9th</td><td>+4</td><td>—</td><td>4</td><td>4</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>1</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>-</td></tr><tr><td>10th</td><td>+4</td><td>Arcane Tradition Feature</td><td>5</td><td>4</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>2</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>-</td></tr><tr><td>11th</td><td>+4</td><td>—</td><td>5</td><td>4</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>2</td><td>1</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>-</td></tr><tr><td>12th</td><td>+4</td><td>Ability Score Improvement</td><td>5</td><td>4</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>2</td><td>1</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>-</td></tr><tr><td>13th</td><td>+5</td><td>—</td><td>5</td><td>4</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>2</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>-</td><td>-</td></tr><tr><td>14th</td><td>+5</td><td>Arcane Tradition Feature</td><td>5</td><td>4</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>2</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>-</td><td>-</td></tr><tr><td>15th</td><td>+5</td><td>—</td><td>5</td><td>4</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>2</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>-</td></tr><tr><td>16th</td><td>+5</td><td>Ability Score Improvement</td><td>5</td><td>4</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>2</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>-</td></tr><tr><td>17th</td><td>+6</td><td>—</td><td>5</td><td>4</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>2</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>1</td></tr><tr><td>18th</td><td>+6</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.pdsXmiIKqHrnV4re]{Spell Mastery}</td><td>5</td><td>4</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>1</td></tr><tr><td>19th</td><td>+6</td><td>Ability Score Improvement</td><td>5</td><td>4</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>2</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>1</td></tr><tr><td>20th</td><td>+6</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.BMEd6cyVFvu4fisg]{Archmage}</td><td>5</td><td>4</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>2</td><td>2</td><td>1</td><td>1</td></tr></tbody></table><h1>Arcane Traditions</h1><p>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.biRwgWsq41CAgXJn]{Bladesinging}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.kVcNZCGVSW7Etaq3]{Chronurgy Magic}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.MufD7epPBnDJxWCv]{Graviturgy Magic}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.HdJaPjNexEz3SDJU]{Order of Scribes}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.yPm17bPYprcKfMtR]{School of Abjuration}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.aGT07NOOILGkai4V]{School of Conjuration}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.RFZGFlewcPZihGXb]{School of Divination}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.KRcBisqwkehBxs1i]{School of Enchantment}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.eN5ZxBs5AmTVgUW0]{School of Evocation}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.fPp8Y7Y61ovyGo6l]{School of Illusion}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.Vm3JGKk9TBow54JG]{School of Necromancy}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.TH0oVbgsid1zw3pU]{School of Transmutation}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.3TqFjtay6PYNFlRx]{War Magic}</p><h1>Multiclassing</h1><p>Should you wish to mulitclass into the wizard, the prerequisites and proficiencies gained are listed below.</p><blockquote><h3>Sorcerer Multiclassing Prerequisites</h3><p><strong>Ability Score Minimum:</strong> As a multiclass character, you must have at least an Intelligence score of 13 to take a level in this class, or to take a level in another class if you are already a wizard.</p></blockquote><blockquote><h3>Sorcerer Multiclassing Spell Slots</h3><p><strong>Spell Slots</strong> Add your levels in the wizardclass to the appropriate levels from other classes to determine your available spell slots.</p></blockquote><p></p>",
